{"tid":1307712,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒教你輕鬆Del83無線假新聞台！同定時收看Now同有線新聞！","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:21:06.000Z","uid":275475,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b43423b20b40e9279e916ee036cf4ee5a75b5f","tid":1307712,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zt9ckgUptTU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fzt9ckgUptTU&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWji3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=a70e593a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zt9ckgUptTU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個愛國愛港連登仔<br />\n我要呼籲各位連登同胞<br />\n全面抵制黃屍台無線新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還警察公道 支持成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咱別讓家長長輩受這個黃屍台83台影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我和諧食飯時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xbm34CL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbm34CL.png&h=ad9e8ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定時收看中立 now新聞有線新聞教學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PRldylSf2FE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPRldylSf2FE&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWji3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=1cadaad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PRldylSf2FE</a>"},{"pid":"344d45872c899c6b71368fabcb8f3e9f17f6d5ed","tid":1307712,"uid":275475,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"詳情：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F02%2F23%2Fhkppl-remove-j5-guide%2Ftop-news%2F&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWji3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=272ff915\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/</a><br />\n<br />\n最近幾個星期，香港經歷咗好多野。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個多事之秋，CCTVB仍然堅持着奶共嘅理念，繼續選擇性報道，誤導無知嘅廢中廢老藍絲香港人，令佢哋以為星期三金鐘係暴動、政府永遠都係啱晒。<br />\n<br />\n為咗抵制呢一啲冇良心嘅傳媒，為咗我哋嘅上一代，為咗我哋最親嘅父母長輩，請立即移除無線新聞台。<br />\n<br />\n刪台詳情請參閱以上連結。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞，事事但但</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d9b3a56902734af449b892ba6390c2037fddfbcf","tid":1307712,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"巴打隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9afbc9c3e602a225b05f03c7f4e54cc26311a","tid":1307712,"uid":11950,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"81台係劇集中間好似都有少少新聞<br />\n但delete埋好似太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a1b34c94d1880f998ec8af499620875b6f7dc8","tid":1307712,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba9afbc9c3e602a225b05f03c7f4e54cc26311a","tid":1307712,"uid":11950,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"81台係劇集中間好似都有少少新聞<br />\n但delete埋好似太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"留返j2比老豆賭馬 睇台灣旅遊節目<br />\nj5 明珠睇下電影乜都夠啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea147cd07fdfaef86bd35dc46e101793d999411","tid":1307712,"uid":124473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1a1b34c94d1880f998ec8af499620875b6f7dc8","tid":1307712,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba9afbc9c3e602a225b05f03c7f4e54cc26311a","tid":1307712,"uid":11950,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"81台係劇集中間好似都有少少新聞<br />\n但delete埋好似太過份<img s